        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29770389/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29770389/" class="">第66页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sicko/" class=" " title="[已注销]">[已注销]</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29770389">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">国家外在体制的变化并不能决定人民的精神态度，只有民族内在的特点才能铭刻于历史之中</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-12-14 18:55</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>国家外在体制的变化并不能决定人民的精神态度，只有民族内在的特点才能铭刻于历史之中</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29770389/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-12-14 18:55
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31611177">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/74995778/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u74995778-2.jpg" alt="潜心观天下之势" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31611177/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
